msgid "#"
msgstr ""

msgid "**DPE enabled**"
msgstr "**开通 DPE 引擎**"

msgid "**DashScope API key**"
msgstr "**百炼 API Key**"

msgid "**Images uploaded to OSS**"
msgstr "**上传图片至 OSS**"

msgid "**MaxCompute enabled**"
msgstr "**开通 MaxCompute**"

msgid "**OSS RAM role authorization**"
msgstr "**OSS RAM 角色授权**"

msgid "1"
msgstr ""

msgid "1. Build input dataset"
msgstr "1. 构建输入数据集"

msgid "2"
msgstr ""

msgid "2. Download, decode, and resize images"
msgstr "2. 图片下载、解码与重采样"

msgid "3"
msgstr ""

msgid "3. Multimodal embedding inference"
msgstr "3. 多模态 Embedding 推理"

msgid "4"
msgstr ""

msgid "4. Persist embeddings to MaxCompute"
msgstr "4. 将 Embedding 结果写入 MaxCompute"

msgid "5"
msgstr ""

msgid "5. Cleanup"
msgstr "5. 资源清理"

msgid "A MaxCompute project with valid Access ID / Access Key."
msgstr "需要一个已开通的 MaxCompute 项目，并具备有效的 Access ID / Access Key。"

msgid ""
"A practical pattern is to standardize the pipeline: download and decode "
"raw files, normalize formats, run semantic understanding, generate "
"labels, extract embeddings, and store vectors in a reusable feature "
"table."
msgstr ""
"一个可复用的生产模式是将链路标准化：下载并解码原始文件、统一格式、执行"
"语义理解、生成标签、提取 Embedding，并将向量写入可复用的特征表。"

msgid "Applicable scenarios"
msgstr "适用场景"

msgid "Ask admin to enable DPE in project."
msgstr "联系管理员在项目中开通 DPE。"

msgid "Background"
msgstr "背景信息"

msgid "Cause"
msgstr "原因"

msgid "Check API key status in DashScope console."
msgstr "在百炼控制台检查 API Key 状态。"

msgid "Configure Role ARN for OSS read access."
msgstr "配置用于 OSS 读取访问的 Role ARN。"

msgid ""
"Create your own OSS bucket and upload the five sample images used by this"
" tutorial."
msgstr "请自行创建 OSS Bucket，并上传本教程使用的五张示例图片。"

msgid "Configure OSS RAM role"
msgstr "配置 OSS RAM 角色"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Refer to the service enablement and authorization section in `OSS "
"mounting and use practices <https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-"
"guide/oss-mounting-and-use-practices>`__ to create an OSS bucket and a "
"RAM role with OSS read permission. In this example, the code only needs "
"the RAM role ARN passed through ``with_fs_mount`` as "
"``storage_options={\"role_arn\": ROLE_ARN}``."
msgstr ""
"请参考 `OSS 挂载及使用实践 <https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-"
"guide/oss-mounting-and-use-practices>`__ 中“开通服务及授权”部分，创建 "
"OSS Bucket 以及具备 OSS 读取权限的 RAM 角色。本示例代码只需要将 RAM Role "
"ARN 通过 ``with_fs_mount`` 的 ``storage_options={\"role_arn\": ROLE_ARN}`"
"` 传入。"

msgid ""
"The service-linked-role step shown in the console guide is not used by "
"this example. If your MaxCompute service has already been enabled, focus "
"on the RAM role and OSS permission configuration needed by ``role_arn``."
msgstr ""
"控制台指南中的“创建服务关联角色”步骤不是本示例代码会用到的内容。如果你"
"的 MaxCompute 服务已经开通，请重点完成 ``role_arn`` 所需的 RAM 角色和 OSS"
" 权限配置。"

msgid ""
"Upload these five images to ``oss://<your_oss_endpoint>/<your_oss_bucket"
">/maxframe-image-demo/`` before running this section. The names in "
"``IMAGE_FILES`` must exactly match the objects in your OSS bucket."
msgstr ""
"运行本节前，请将这五张图片上传到 ``oss://<your_oss_endpoint>/<your_oss_"
"bucket>/maxframe-image-demo/``。``IMAGE_FILES`` 中的文件名必须和 OSS "
"Bucket 中的对象名完全一致。"

msgid ""
"For large-scale production workloads, request higher API concurrency "
"limits to avoid 429/403 throttling. If the task times out, open LogView "
"first and check whether OSS mount, image file names, RAM role "
"permissions, and DashScope network access are all valid."
msgstr ""
"在大规模生产任务中，建议申请更高 API 并发配额以避免 429/403 限流。如果"
"任务超时，请优先打开 LogView，检查 OSS 挂载、图片文件名、RAM 角色权限以及"
"百炼网络访问是否正确。"

msgid "Content understanding, moderation, and quality analysis."
msgstr "内容理解、审核与质量分析。"

msgid "Core workflow"
msgstr "核心处理流程"

msgid "Create an API key for multimodal embedding calls."
msgstr "创建用于多模态 Embedding 调用的 API Key。"

msgid ""
"Create or manage your API key in DashScope console: `DashScope API Key "
"management <https://bailian.console.aliyun.com/cn-beijing?tab=model#/api-"
"key>`__."
msgstr ""
"前往 `百炼控制台 - API Key 管理 <https://bailian.console.aliyun.com/cn-"
"beijing?tab=model#/api-key>`__ 创建或管理 API Key。"

msgid "DPE is not enabled"
msgstr "未开通 DPE"

msgid "DashScope API key management page"
msgstr "百炼控制台 API Key 管理页面"

msgid "Data preparation for RAG, knowledge base, and agent applications."
msgstr "为 RAG、知识库与 Agent 应用准备多模态数据。"

msgid "Deduplication and clustering using vector similarity."
msgstr "基于向量相似度进行去重与聚类。"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

msgid "Different embedding models were mixed"
msgstr "混用了不同的 Embedding 模型"

msgid "Embedding is ``None``"
msgstr "Embedding 结果为 ``None``"

msgid ""
"Enterprise data platforms increasingly rely on multimodal data such as "
"images, text, audio, and video. These data assets are often heterogeneous"
" and unstructured, making them difficult to use directly for search, "
"recommendation, moderation, clustering, and analytics."
msgstr ""
"企业数据平台越来越多地使用图片、文本、音频和视频等多模态数据。这些数据"
"通常格式异构、结构化程度低，难以直接支撑检索、推荐、审核、聚类和分析等"
"下游场景。"

msgid "Environment setup"
msgstr "环境准备"

msgid "Feature generation for recommendation and ranking systems."
msgstr "为推荐与排序系统生产图像特征。"

msgid ""
"For large-scale production workloads, request higher API concurrency "
"limits to avoid 429/403 throttling."
msgstr "在大规模生产任务中，建议申请更高 API 并发配额以避免 429/403 限流。"

msgid "Get DashScope API key"
msgstr "获取百炼 API Key"

msgid "Image operators and ``apply_chunk`` run on DPE."
msgstr "Image 算子与 ``apply_chunk`` 在 DPE 上执行。"

msgid "Image processing and embedding workflow"
msgstr "图像处理与 Embedding 流程"

msgid "Inconsistent vector dimensions"
msgstr "向量维度不一致"

msgid "Invalid API key"
msgstr "API Key 无效"

msgid "Issue"
msgstr "问题"

msgid "Multimodal Image Feature Pipeline with MaxFrame"
msgstr "多模态图像特征生产方案"

msgid "Multimodal retrieval and similar-content recall."
msgstr "多模态检索与相似内容召回。"

msgid "Per-image inference failure"
msgstr "单张图片推理失败"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前提条件"

msgid "**MaxFrame SDK version**"
msgstr "**MaxFrame SDK 版本**"

msgid "Use MaxFrame SDK **2.6.0** or above (``pip install maxframe>=2.6.0``)."
msgstr ""
"请使用 MaxFrame SDK **2.6.0** 及以上版本（``pip install maxframe>=2.6.0``"
"）。"

msgid "Requirement"
msgstr "条件"

msgid "Resolution"
msgstr "解决方案"

msgid "Reusable feature asset construction for enterprise data governance."
msgstr "构建可复用的企业级图像特征资产。"

msgid "Source images are in a target OSS bucket."
msgstr "原始图片已上传至目标 OSS Bucket。"

msgid ""
"This tutorial demonstrates a multimodal image feature pipeline on "
"MaxFrame: distributed image preprocessing, semantic embedding inference, "
"and table persistence for downstream retrieval, recommendation, "
"moderation, clustering, and analytics."
msgstr ""
"本方案依托 MaxFrame 的分布式处理能力，演示一条面向多场景复用的图像特征"
"生产链路：批量预处理图像、调用多模态模型生成语义 Embedding，并将结果写入"
"表中，供检索、推荐、审核、聚类和分析等下游任务使用。"

msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题排查"

msgid "Use one embedding model per batch/output table."
msgstr "同一批次或输出表请使用同一 Embedding 模型。"

msgid "Verify ``role_arn`` and OSS read permissions."
msgstr "检查 ``role_arn`` 与 OSS 读取权限配置。"

msgid "Verify image integrity and base64 generation."
msgstr "检查图片完整性与 base64 编码结果。"

msgid "Wrong or missing role permissions"
msgstr "角色权限错误或缺失"

msgid "``Engine DPE not available``"
msgstr ""

